'''''100 Days'''''  ni film yikinamico 2001 iyobowe na Nick Hughes ikorwa na Hughes na Eric Kabera . Iyi filime ni ikinamico y'ibyabaye mu gihe cya [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside yo]] mu Rwanda mu 1994. Umutwe wa filime werekeza ku buryo butaziguye igihe cyashize kuva jenoside yatangira ku ya 6 Mata kugeza kirangiye hagati muri Nyakanga 1994.

Iyi filime niyo filime ya mbere yakinnye yakozwe kuri jenoside yo mu 1994 kandi yibanda ku buzima [[Abatutsi|bw’umukobwa ukiri muto, w’impunzi w’abatutsi]] ndetse n’uko yagerageje gushaka umutekano mu gihe jenoside ikorwa.  Yarasiwe ahantu Genocide yo mu Rwanda yabereye. 
